%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20drama%20could%20quickly%20become%20Big%20Tech's%20problem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223329%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Big%20Tech%20logos%20with%20dollar%20signs%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f11fe429fef86fd43d3c2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222497%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20post%20originally%20appeared%20in%20the%20Business%20Insider%20Today%20newsletter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finsider-today%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20daily%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20pressure%2C%20but%20five%20companies%20carrying%20the%20market%20report%20earnings%20over%20the%20next%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlphabet%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20all%20report%20today%20after%20the%20bell.%20Apple%20closes%20things%20out%20on%20Thursday.%20In%20total%2C%20more%20than%20%2415%20trillion%20in%20market%20capitalization%20is%20telling%20investors%20how%20they're%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20massive%20size%20isn't%20the%20only%20important%20thing.%20Since%20almost%20all%20these%20companies%20are%20vying%20for%20AI%20supremacy%2C%20their%20success%20(or%20failure)%20is%20a%20report%20card%20on%20the%20technology%20reshaping%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI's%20Joe%20Ciolli%2C%20author%20of%20the%20great%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ffirst-trade%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFirst%20Trade%20newsletter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20breaks%20down%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-preview-key-numbers-alphabet-microsoft-amazon-meta-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20to%20look%20out%20for%20with%20each%20company%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We've%20also%20got%20analyst%20roundups%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-q1-earnings-preview-aws-amzn-stock-ai-capex-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-q1-earnings-preview-ai-revenue-growth-capex-wall-street-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20private%20company's%20reported%20challenges%20are%20also%20weighing%20heavily%20on%20these%20public%20giants.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20story%20from%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fai%2Fopenai-misses-key-revenue-user-targets-in-high-stakes-sprint-toward-ipo-94a95273%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20missing%20key%20revenue%20and%20user%20targets%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-missed-targets-what-smart-people-are-saying-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20investors%20spooked%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Public%20companies%20directly%20partnering%20with%20OpenAI%20%E2%80%94%20like%20CoreWeave%20and%20Oracle%20%E2%80%94%20took%20the%20brunt%20of%20it.%20But%20the%20impact%20was%20felt%20across%20the%20tech%20sector.%20The%20Nasdaq%20100%20index%20finished%20down%201%25%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WSJ%20reports%20that%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20and%20CFO%20Sarah%20Friar%20don't%20see%20eye%20to%20eye%20over%20the%20AI%20giant's%20massive%20data-center%20spending%20ahead%20of%20a%20potential%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20Altman%20and%20Friar%20called%20the%20story%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20reports%20have%20surfaced%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-new-yorker-profile-character-information-cfo-policy-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20two%20don't%20get%20along%3C%2Fa%3E.%20BI's%20Peter%20Kafka%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-ipo-cfo-sarah-friar-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreaks%20it%20all%20down%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI's%20Alistair%20Barr%2C%20author%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETech%20Memo%20newsletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20(another%20great%20one)%2C%20found%20the%20recent%20reports%20strange%20to%20read.%20While%20concerns%20about%20OpenAI's%20heavy%20compute%20spending%20persist%2C%20its%20aggressive%20push%20to%20lock%20in%20capacity%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-won-ai-compute-race-business-model-next-anthropic-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enow%20looks%20pragmatic%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20rivals%20like%20Anthropic%20face%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-compute-limits-anthropic-github-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutages%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenclaw-ai-demand-token-use-surge-nvidia-pricing-jumps-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20pains%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Alistair%20writes.%20But%20the%20bigger%20challenge%20isn't%20just%20building%20powerful%20AI%2C%20it's%20figuring%20out%20who%20will%20pay%20for%20it%2C%20and%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20reported%20dispute%20between%20a%20CEO%20and%20CFO%20over%20spending%20seems%20very%20specific%20to%20that%20company.%20But%20a%20lot%20of%20OpenAI's%20challenges%20are%20what%20the%20wider%20tech%20industry%20is%20facing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20almost%20every%20Big%20Tech%20company%20can't%20stop%20talking%20about%20how%20much%20they're%20spending%20on%20AI.%20And%20just%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20whenever%20they%20get%20pressed%20on%20that%20approach%2C%20they%20all%20say%20the%20risk%20of%20overspending%20is%20far%20smaller%20than%20the%20risk%20of%20underspending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20OpenAI%20is%20facing%20budgetary%20pressure%2C%20what%20does%20that%20say%20about%20the%20rest%20of%20Big%20Tech%20that's%20followed%20suit%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20giants%20benefit%20from%20having%20established%20businesses%20besides%20AI%20that%20generate%20substantial%20revenue.%20Still%2C%20they've%20all%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20their%20future%20is%20all%20about%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20the%20math%20ain't%20working%20for%20OpenAI%2C%20how%20long%20until%20the%20numbers%20don't%20work%20for%20Big%20Tech%20either%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-impact-from-openai-revenue-reports-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777470227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f11fe429fef86fd43d3c2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-impact-from-openai-revenue-reports-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Big%20Tech's%20earnings%20spotlight%20AI%20investments%2C%20but%20OpenAI's%20reported%20revenue%20and%20user%20struggles%20could%20complicate%20things.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20chefs%20share%20how%20generative%20AI%20helps%20them%20manage%20menu%20changes%20and%20event%20logistics%20on%20their%20own%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meenu%20Bhasin%20and%20Melanie%20Underwood%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef7e55a98bc8fdc096f47d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeenu%20Bhasin%20(l)%20and%20Melanie%20Underwood%20each%20operate%20their%20own%20cooking%20company%2C%20and%20have%20found%20ways%20to%20use%20AI%20for%20operational%20help.%3Cp%3ECayce%20Clifford%20and%20Marissa%20Alper%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeenu%20Bhasin%20and%20Melanie%20Underwood%20operate%20solo%20cooking%20companies%2C%20with%20some%20help%20from%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20AI%20helps%20them%20research%20ingredients%2C%20plan%20events%2C%20and%20develop%20social%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20chefs%20said%20AI%20can't%20replace%20the%20human%20touch%20in%20teaching%20and%20tasting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20hour%20before%20a%20recent%20private%20cooking%20class%2C%20chef%20and%20solopreneur%20Meenu%20Bhasin%20got%20a%20message%3A%20one%20of%20the%20children%20attending%20had%20a%20severe%20egg%20allergy.%20Two%20of%20her%20planned%20recipes%20required%20eggs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20said%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20cancel%2C%20we%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhasin%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20staff%20to%20help%20her%2C%20she%20opened%20ChatGPT%2C%20typed%20in%20every%20ingredient%20she%20had%20on%20hand%2C%20and%20asked%20it%20to%20come%20up%20with%20two%20simple%2C%20egg-free%20recipes%20for%20young%20children.%20%26quot%3BIt%20delivered%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBefore%20ChatGPT%2C%20that%20would%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20stress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20one%20of%20the%20many%20ways%20that%20Bhasin%20and%20another%20chef%2C%20Melanie%20Underwood%20of%20Nourish%20%26amp%3B%20Gather%2C%20use%20generative%20AI%20for%20behind-the-scenes%20operational%20support%20in%20their%20solo%20cooking%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fthe-ai-powered-solopreneur%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20AI-Powered%20Solopreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20series%20explores%20how%20solo%20business%20owners%20use%20AI%20to%20drive%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c5bc435-f7bc-42bf-ae69-63a68f6b3d87%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETailoring%20client%20experiences%20with%20generative%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Bhasin%2C%20who%20has%20run%20her%20Bay%20Area%20cooking%20company%20for%20more%20than%2015%20years%2C%20much%20of%20her%20time%20preparing%20for%20classes%20is%20spent%20building%20menus%20that%20cater%20to%20a%20unique%20combination%20of%20dietary%20restrictions%2C%20preferences%2C%20and%20kitchen%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20she%20started%20using%20ChatGPT%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago%2C%20the%20process%20has%20become%20more%20streamlined%2C%20Bhasin%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meenu%20Bhasin%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef7ecda98bc8fdc096f481%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBhasin%20uses%20AI%20for%20ideas%20when%20she's%20looking%20to%20swap%20ingredients.%3Cp%3ECayce%20Clifford%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBhasin%20said%20she%20might%20get%20an%20email%20from%20a%20group%20that%20has%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20dietary%20needs%20and%20tastes%2C%20from%20pescatarians%20to%20gluten%20free%2C%20and%20she%20has%20to%20create%20an%20experience%20that%20will%20work%20for%20everyone.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20like%2C%20'oh%20my%20goodness%2C%20ChatGPT%2C%20what%20can%20I%20teach%20this%20group%3F%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe'll%20also%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20research%20ingredient%20swaps%2C%20such%20as%20finding%20alternatives%20to%20sesame%20seeds%20and%20soy%20sauce%20that%20still%20deliver%20the%20salty%2C%20spicy%2C%20and%20sweet%20notes%20essential%20to%20an%20Asian%20cooking%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Bhasin%20said%20the%20final%20call%20is%20always%20hers.%20%26quot%3BIt%20gives%20me%20the%20legwork%2C%20and%20then%20I%20have%20to%20go%20in%2C%20use%20those%20ingredients%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20it%20actually%20tastes%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderwood%2C%20a%20Westchester-based%20culinary%20educator%20and%20chef%2C%20said%20she%20also%20uses%20AI%20to%20tailor%20her%20standard%20program%20materials%20for%20different%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20recently%20ran%20her%20nutrition%20program%20for%20a%20group%20of%20eight%20men%20in%20a%20corporate%20setting%2C%20she%20asked%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20to%20help%20her%20reframe%20the%20content%20with%20a%20more%20data-driven%20lens.%20Underwood%20said%20she%20always%20double%20checks%20the%20studies%20that%20Claude%20cites%20before%20using%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6c91861-8bc3-4f3c-85b9-c4f8606532a9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20lessens%20the%20load%20of%20event%20management%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnderwood%20said%20that%20generative%20AI%20has%20been%20especially%20useful%20for%20planning%20her%20cooking%20workshops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe'll%20upload%20her%20recipes%20to%20Claude%2C%20tell%20it%20the%20number%20of%20participants%2C%20then%20prompt%20it%20to%20multiply%20the%20recipe%20ingredients%20and%20list%20out%20which%20equipment%20she%20needs%20to%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20so%20helpful%20for%20scalability%2C%20because%20then%20I'm%20actually%20not%20having%20to%20sit%20and%20write%20out%20all%20of%20those%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Underwood%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20allows%20her%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20the%20creative%20side%20of%20her%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2211250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Melanie%20Underwood%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef7f233fecbb42897a48da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnderwood%20said%20AI%20has%20been%20helpful%20when%20planning%20workshops.%3Cp%3EMarissa%20Alper%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBhasin%20said%20that%20AI%20helps%20her%20better%20manage%20client%20communications%2C%20which%20often%20requires%20her%20to%20email%20each%20group%20back%20and%20forth%20several%20times%20before%20their%20class.%20Generative%20AI%20helps%20her%20work%20through%20her%20thoughts%20around%20specific%20requests%20and%20draft%20difficult%20messages%20in%20a%20diplomatic%20tone%2C%20Bhasin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20five%20parents%20recently%20asked%20her%20to%20change%20an%20already-advertised%20summer%20camp%20menu%20to%20suit%20their%20children%2C%20she%20consulted%20ChatGPT%20before%20responding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChatGPT%20asked%20me%3A%20'What%20is%20your%20goal%20here%3F%20Is%20it%20to%20make%20as%20much%20money%20as%20possible%2C%20or%20is%20it%20to%20teach%20a%20high-quality%20camp%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20those%20questions%20in%20mind%2C%20Bhasin%20revisited%20her%20initial%20reasons%20for%20choosing%20the%20planned%20theme.%20Ultimately%2C%20that%20process%20led%20her%20to%20decide%20not%20to%20alter%20the%20menu%20to%20preserve%20the%20reputation%20her%20classes%20are%20known%20for%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meenu%20Bhasin%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef805d3fecbb42897a48e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBhasin%20said%20AI%20will%20never%20replace%20a%20chef's%20human%20touch.%3Cp%3ECayce%20Clifford%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c43bd922-0fbe-4ee4-8898-539e89954025%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlanning%20for%20the%20future%20with%20AI%20assistance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20solopreneurs%20have%20also%20used%20AI%20as%20a%20thinking%20partner%20to%20grow%20their%20businesses%20in%20ways%20they%20said%20they%20couldn't%20have%20managed%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Underwood%2C%20that%20meant%20turning%20a%20viral%20moment%20into%20a%20new%20revenue%20stream.%20When%20an%20Instagram%20Reel%20she%20posted%20generated%2030%20DMs%20in%20a%20single%20day%2C%20she%20knew%20she'd%20hit%20on%20something%2C%20but%20wasn't%20sure%20how%20to%20organize%20her%20ideas.%20%26quot%3BIt%20helped%20me%20very%20strategically%20sort%20of%20plan%20the%20framework%20for%20what%20I%20already%20had%20in%20my%20brain%20%E2%80%94%20putting%20it%20out%20in%20a%20written%20form%20that%20I%20probably%20couldn't%20have%20done%20without%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20The%20result%20was%20the%20Family%20Table%20Reset%2C%20a%20six-month%20virtual%20program%20for%20parents%20that%20has%20since%20become%20a%20core%20part%20of%20her%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBhasin%20said%20that%20with%20AI's%20recipe%20brainstorming%20support%2C%20she%20anticipates%20having%20enough%20ideas%20to%20teach%20two%20new%20recipes%20a%20week%20for%20the%20next%2010%20to%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2211013%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Melanie%20Underwood%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef80d83fecbb42897a48e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnderwood%20was%20able%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20a%20viral%20social%20moment.%3Cp%3EMarissa%20Alper%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20experiencing%20the%20benefits%20of%20generative%20AI%20in%20their%20businesses%2C%20both%20chefs%20said%20there%20are%20food-focused%20tasks%20that%20AI%20simply%20can't%20do%3A%20Developing%2C%20tasting%2C%20and%20teaching%20delicious%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20enhances%20what%20I%20do%3B%20it%20can%20never%20replace%20chefs%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhasin%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20that%20human%20touch.%20You%20need%20my%20vibrant%20personality.%20You%20need%20that%20passion.%20And%20that%20only%20comes%20through%20when%20you've%20got%20a%20real%20person%20teaching%20you%20a%20class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwo-chefs-running-solo-companies-tap-ai-for-operational-help-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777470195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef7e55a98bc8fdc096f47d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwo-chefs-running-solo-companies-tap-ai-for-operational-help-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chefs%20Meenu%20Bhasin%20and%20Melanie%20Underwood%20run%20their%20solo%20cooking%20companies%20using%20AI%20tools%20to%20streamline%20operations%20and%20enhance%20client%20experiences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Greenawald)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20to%20watch%20Atletico%20Madrid%20vs.%20Arsenal%20for%20free%3A%20Champions%20League%20live%20stream%2C%20channels%2C%20start%20time%2C%20odds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222844%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Declan%20Rice%20of%20Arsenal%20appears%20dejected%20on%20a%20soccer%20field%20during%20a%202026%20Premier%20League%20match.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f110283b4f7c3af2b7ac9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221422%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArsenal%20will%20face%20Atle