utube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fd-O34WXXEQA%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22NextGen%20Acela%20Has%20Arrived%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EEliot%20Hamlisch%2C%20Amtrak's%20chief%20commercial%20officer%2C%20said%20the%20bulk%20of%20its%20current%20marketing%20output%20is%20about%20helping%20the%20traveling%20public%20see%20passenger%20rail%20as%20a%20preferred%20mode%20of%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20stuck%20in%20traffic%20on%20the%20I-95%2C%20you're%20not%20stuck%20in%20a%20middle%20seat%20while%20circling%20above%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmisery-map-shows-where-flight-cancellations-airports-snowstorm-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EReagan%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20able%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamlisch%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Fcmo-insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Amtrak%20is%20taking%20%26quot%3Ba%20really%20bold%20and%20very%20confident%20approach%20to%20the%20messaging%2C%20the%20creative%2C%20the%20music%2C%20to%20help%20highlight%20those%20amenities%20and%20benefits%20that%20differentiate%20this%20train%20relative%20to%20cars%20and%20planes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Build%26quot%3B%20ad%2C%20part%20of%20its%20broader%20long-running%20%26quot%3BRetrain%20Travel%26quot%3B%20campaign%2C%20debuts%20on%20linear%20TV%20during%20the%20Kentucky%20Derby%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22330253fb-be42-4e15-82c2-076a702ce58d%5C%22%3EAmtrak's%20advertising%20outlay%3A%20the%20numbers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2080%25%20of%20Amtrak's%20ad%20spending%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Build%26quot%3B%20is%20directed%20toward%20%26quot%3Bawareness%20driving%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20TV%2C%20digital%20video%2C%20and%20podcasts%2C%20versus%2020%25%20of%20ads%20designed%20to%20prompt%20people%20to%20buy%20a%20ticket%20immediately%2C%20Hamlisch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20quarter%20(26%25)%20of%20US%20adults%20in%20data-intelligence%20firm%20Morning%20Consult's%20latest%20nationwide%20survey%20said%20they%20would%20consider%20becoming%20Amtrak%20customers%2C%20up%20slightly%20from%2023%25%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Famtraks-new-marketing-strategy-its-not-a-train-its-a-hotel-on-wheels-aef63302%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BRetrain%20Travel%26quot%3B%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20kicked%20off%20in%202024.%20Brand%20awareness%20has%20remained%20at%2083%25%20since%202024%2C%20Morning%20Consult%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmtrak's%20ad%20spend%20is%20low%20compared%20to%20airlines%20and%20automakers.%20The%20quasi-public%20national%20rail%20service%20spent%20%2436%20million%20on%20advertising%20in%202025%2C%20down%20from%20%2439%20million%20a%20year%20earlier%2C%20even%20as%20ticket%20revenue%20rose%2010%25%20to%20%242.7%20billion.%20Hamlisch%20said%20he%20anticipates%20the%20company's%20ad%20spend%20will%20stay%20at%20a%20similar%20level%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20marketing%20is%20focused%20less%20on%20winning%20market%20share%20and%20more%20on%20introducing%20its%20new%20Acela%20fleet%20and%20reshaping%20perceptions%20of%20train%20travel%20among%20people%20who%20may%20have%20only%20historically%20considered%20flying%20or%20driving%20between%20major%20city%20centers%20on%20its%20Northeast%20corridor%20routes%2C%20Hamlisch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20numbers%20benchmarked%20against%20airline%20data%20show%20that%20Amtrak%20has%20an%2080%25%20market%20share%20of%20trips%20between%20New%20York%20City%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20a%2065%25%20share%20between%20New%20York%20City%20and%20Boston%2C%20Hamlisch%20said.%20It%20has%20lower%20penetration%20on%20its%20slower%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-mistakes-first-long-distance-ride%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-distance%20routes%3C%2Fa%3E%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmtrak%20has%20been%20steadily%20ramping%20up%20its%20social%20presence%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20convert%20Gen%20Z%20to%20train%20travel.%20Last%20July%2C%20an%20Amtrak%20video%20spoofing%20retro%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emarketer.com%2Fcontent%2Fhow-amtrak-monster-truck-inspired-viral-video-fostered-audience-growth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonster%20truck%20rally%3C%2Fa%3E%20TV%20ads%20went%20viral%20across%20platforms%20like%20Instagram%20and%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FnrfmRGIls4o%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Summer%20Train-tacular%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20something%20you%20would%20ever%20have%20anticipated%20seeing%20come%20through%20an%20Amtrak%20social%20channel%2C%20or%20any%20other%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamlisch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f2463b7-7736-4f02-b292-f039f35263d8%5C%22%3ERail's%20momentum%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmtrak%20is%20riding%20strong%20momentum.%20Ridership%20hit%20a%20record%2034.4%20million%20trips%20in%20its%202025%20fiscal%20year%2C%20which%20ended%20in%20September%2C%20up%205%25%20year%20over%20year.%20The%20rail%20service%20aims%20to%20nearly%20double%20that%20to%2066%20million%20annually%20by%202040%20as%20it%20upgrades%20tracks%2C%20stations%2C%20and%20trains.%20(That%20number%20is%20still%20small%20compared%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Metropolitan%20Transit%20Authority%2C%20which%20saw%20nearly%201.9%20billion%20annual%20trips%20as%20of%20late%202025%20across%20the%20subway%2C%20buses%2C%20and%20paratransit.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmtrak%20was%20a%20major%20beneficiary%20of%20the%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhats-in-the-infrastructure-bill-amtrak-clean-energy-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebipartisan%20infrastructure%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20gave%20it%20about%20%2422%20billion%20over%20five%20years%20to%20upgrade%20and%20modernize%20its%20service.%20It%20received%20a%20further%20boost%20in%20April%2C%20when%20the%20Trump%20administration%20announced%20a%20%244.7%20billion%20investment%20in%20rail%20projects%20along%20Amtrak's%20Northeast%20Corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20tailwind%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F20-hour-amtrak-over-flight-to-avoid-airport-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAir%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20has%20been%20a%20mess%20for%20the%20past%20several%20months%2C%20prompting%20some%20passengers%20to%20consider%20taking%20the%20train%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20certainly%20don't%20aim%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20by%20dialing%20up%20marketing%20in%20response%2C%20Hamlisch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20is%20steadily%20rolling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-coach-business-class-comparison-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eupgraded%20Acela%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20supported%20by%20its%20aspirational%20ad%20campaign%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20Amtrak%20fleet%20is%20aging%2C%20with%20the%20average%20railcar%20about%2033%20years%20old%2C%20per%20a%202024%20Bureau%20of%20Transportation%20Statistics%20report.%20Plus%2C%20Amtrak%20must%20manage%20delays%20and%20disruptions%20that%20come%20with%20improvement%20works%20to%20old%20tracks%2C%20bridges%2C%20and%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManaging%20customer%20expectations%20is%20arguably%20the%20No.%201%20thing%20that%20I%20wake%20up%20thinking%20about%20each%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamlisch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-spoofs-luxury-car-ads-convince-travellers-take-train-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777464001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1a4e729fef86fd43d3d9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-spoofs-luxury-car-ads-convince-travellers-take-train-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amtrak%20wants%20to%20shift%20America's%20%26quot%3Bcar-first%20mindset%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20chief%20commercial%20officer%2C%20Eliot%20Hamlisch%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CW%20Sports%20to%20Stream%20Via%20ESPN%20in%20Unique%20Content%20Pact%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777464000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236732888%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Approximately%20800%20hours%20of%20college%20football%20and%20basketball%2C%20professional%20bull%20riding%2C%20WWE%20action%2C%20NASCAR%20races%2C%20PBA%20bowling%20and%20professional%20volleyball%20that%20air%20each%20year%20on%20Nexstar%E2%80%99s%20CW%20broadcast%20network%20will%20steam%20from%20a%20venue%20that%20might%20be%20considered%20surprising%3A%20ESPN.%20Under%20a%20deal%20announced%20Wednesday%2C%20ESPN%20will%20reap%20the%20extra%20hours%20of%20activity%20and%20the%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Brian%20Steinberg%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20went%20on%20a%20river%20cruise%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20our%202%20young%20kids.%20It%20totally%20changed%20my%20perspective%20on%20cruising.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20with%20sunglasses%20smilin%20on%20river%20cruise%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efce52a98bc8fdc096f728%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20an%20anti-cruise%20family.%20After%20taking%20my%20first%20river%20cruise%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20I%20can't%20stop%20talking%20about%20it.%3Cp%3EMary%20Kearl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20family%20that%20loved%20to%20go%20on%20big%20trips%2C%20but%20refused%20to%20travel%20by%20cruise%20ship.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20went%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-river-cruise-surprisingly-good-loved-itinerary-accommodations-2025-10%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20river%20cruise%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%2040%20with%20my%20family%20and%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20I%20enjoyed%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThough%20I'm%20still%20not%20sure%20if%20I%20would%20go%20on%20an%20open-ocean%20cruise%2C%20I've%20become%20a%20river%20cruise%20convert.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20are%20so%20anti-cruise%20that%20when%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-visit-alaska-from-man-visited-all-50-states-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisited%20Alaska%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20my%2021st%20birthday%2C%20we%20took%20a%20series%20of%20planes%2C%20trains%2C%20automobiles%2C%20and%20ferries%20to%20experience%20what%20a%20cruise%20would%20have%20made%20possible%20with%20a%20lot%20less%20planning%20and%20logistics%20on%20our%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I'm%20older%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20finally%20give%20cruising%20a%20real%20try.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20both%20turning%2040%20this%20year%2C%20I%20wanted%20us%20to%20take%20an%20epic%20trip%20to%20celebrate%2C%20and%20I%20set%20my%20sights%20on%20a%20four-day%2C%20three-night%20Nile%20River%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20enjoyed%20short%20excursions%20on%20rivers%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-affordable-places-to-visit-next-year-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDouro%20River%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Portugal%20to%20the%20Amazon%20River%20in%20Brazil%2C%20I%20suspected%20that%20I'd%20like%20the%20experience.%20It%20did%20not%20disappoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20coming%20back%20from%20the%20trip%20we%20took%20in%20mid-February%2C%20I%20can't%20stop%20talking%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freasons-not-like-river-cruises-cons-from-someone-who-loves-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eriver%20cruises%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20and%20strangers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f350d21-315d-4aad-987f-ef97a6d317bc%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20experience%20many%20common%20issues%20ocean%20cruisers%20complain%20about%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22river%20cruise%20in%20water%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efce53367066d7c2971a81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20like%20the%20smaller%20size%20of%20river%20cruises.%3Cp%3EMary%20Kearl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sailed%20on%20the%20Lilac%20Nile%20Cruises%20H-S%20Moondance%2C%20a%20ship%20with%2058%20double%20cabins%20and%20eight%20suites%20and%20a%20capacity%20for%20up%20to%20about%20132%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20mere%20fraction%20of%20the%20guests%20you'll%20find%20on%20major%20ocean%20cruises%20with%20lines%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-solo-cruise-surprises%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERoyal%20Caribbean%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Carnival%2C%20where%20massive%20ships%20accommodate%20anywhere%20from%201%2C900%20to%20more%20than%205%2C000%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20few%20dozen%20passengers%2C%20only%20four%20floors%2C%20and%20a%20few%20amenities%20%E2%80%94%20a%20roof-deck%20with%20a%20pool%2C%20a%20lounge%20area%2C%20a%20gym%2C%20a%20gift%20shop%2C%20a%20spa%2C%20and%20one%20buffet-style%20dining%20room%20%E2%80%94%20this%20ship%20didn't%20feel%20like%20anything%20like%20the%20stereotypical%20%26quot%3Bgiant%20floating%20resort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20smaller%20size%20also%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20walk%20around%20the%20ship%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20some%20of%20the%20common%20issues%20I%20hear%20about%20from%20cruisers%2C%20like%20crowded%20buffets%20and%20fights%20to%20reserve%20deck%20chairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20rarely%20had%20to%20wait%20in%20lines%20for%20the%20buffet%2C%20and%20when%20we%20went%20to%20the%20roof-deck%2C%20we%20easily%20found%20loungers%20and%20often%20had%20the%20pool%20to%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20weren't%20out%20and%20about%2C%20we%20were%20in%20our%20spacious%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20triple%20room%20included%20a%20king%20bed%20for%20my%20husband%20and%20me%2C%20a%20single%20bed%20for%20our%20oldest%20daughter%2C%20and%20space%20for%20a%20pack-and-play%20for%20our%201-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20even%20had%20a%20table%20and%20chair%2C%20a%20mini%20fridge%2C%20two%20closets%20that%20fit%20our%20three%20suitcases%20with%20room%20to%20spare%2C%20and%20a%20compact%20shower-bathtub%20combo%20in%20the%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Friver-cruise-boom-and-viking-river-cruises-2014-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETraditional%20river%20cruises%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20have%20interior%20cabins%2C%20so%20every%20room%20has%20a%20view%2C%20including%20ours.%20Our%20accommodations%20also%20felt%20surprisingly%20spacious%2C%20in%20part%20because%20there%20were%20so%20few%20cabins%20on%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0f3b45e-a8c1-4095-9f52-773329fde9d3%5C%22%3EBeing%20on%20a%20river%20was%20quite%20calming%20and%20good%20for%20my%20peace%20of%20mind%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20sitting%20by%20pool%20on%20rooftop%20deck%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efce533fecbb42897a4b6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20took%20advantage%20of%20the%20pool%20on%20the%20roof-deck.%3Cp%3EMary%20Kearl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20experienced%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-river-cruise-surprisingly-good-loved-itinerary-accommodations-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebenefits%20of%20sailing%20on%20a%20river%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20much%20calmer%20than%20the%20ocean.%20None%20of%20us%20%E2%80%94%20not%20even%20my%208-year-old%20and%20husband%2C%20who%20are%20prone%20to%20motion%20sickness%20and%20have%20gotten%20ill%20on%20much%20shorter%20boat%20rides%20%E2%80%94%20ever%20felt%20nauseous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20came%20home%2C%20my%20daughter%20even%20said%20she%20missed%20the%20feeling%20of%20falling%20asleep%20on%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20felt%20better%20being%20on%20a%20river%2C%20especially%20with%20small%20kids.%20For%20one%2C%20since%20my%20youngest%20doesn't%20know%20how%20to%20swim%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20being%20in%20the%20open%20sea%20made%20me%20especially%20anxious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20don't%20like%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20stuck%2C%20surrounded%20on%20all%20sides%20by%20water%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20sea.%20On%20the%20river%20cruise%2C%20being%20able%20to%20see%20land%20at%20all%20times%20gave%20me%20peace%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20I%20never%20feel%20trapped%2C%20but%20I%20also%20felt%20confident%20that%20if%20an%20emergency%20happened%20with%20either%20of%20our%20kids%2C%20we%20could%20get%20help%20fairly%20quickly%20and%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220475487-dfba-4cfe-88a6-0eafb4333a22%5C%22%3EOur%20itinerary%20kept%20us%20busy%20but%20gave%20us%20lots%20of%20time%20for%20relaxation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kid%20in%20egypt%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efce533fecbb42897a4b69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlthough%20we%20might%20not%20have%20seen%20Egypt%20like%20locals%2C%20we%20fit%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20sightseeing.%3Cp%3EMary%20Kearl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20nice%20thing%20about%20river%20cruises%20is%20that%20some%20excursions%20are%20generally%20included%20in%20the%20cost%2C%20which%20isn't%20common%20on%20ocean%20sailings.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20we%20were%20traveling%20with%20small%20children%2C%20we%20only%20opted%20for%20one%20excursion%20per%20day%2C%20which%20was%20included%20in%20the%20price%20of%20our%20trip.%20If%20we%20wanted%2C%20we%20could%20have%20gone%20on%20two%20outings%20per%20day%20for%20an%20added%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20was%2C%20we%20saw%20plenty%20of%20incredible%20historic%20sites%20and%20got%20to%20try%20a%20mix%20of%20international%20and%20local%20cuisine%20throughout%20our%20time%20on%20land%20and%20on%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22buffet%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efce523fecbb42897a4b66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20had%20plenty%20of%20options%20for%20food%20on%20the%20ship.%3Cp%3EMary%20Kearl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sampled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpapyrus-paper-making-egypt-al-qaramous-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEgyptian%20desserts%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20day%2C%20I%20ate%20several%20different%20local%20salads%20at%20each%20lunch%20and%20dinner%2C%20and%20I%20even%20got%20my%20falafel%20fix%20one%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlanned%20activities%20aside%2C%20finding%20myself%20poolside%20on%20a%20roof-deck%20with%20good%20weather%20and%20idyllic%20views%20is%20my%20idea%20of%20paradise%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20river%20cruise%20I%20went%20on%20allowed%20me%20to%20pass%20plenty%20of%20blissful%20hours%20soaking%20in%20the%20Egyptian%20countryside%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20a%20lounge%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20family%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20plenty%20of%20swimming%2C%20playing%2C%20and%20taking%20in%20the%20scenery%20together%20up%20on%20the%20roof-deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rooftop%20pool%20deck%20with%20covered%20loungers%20nearby%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efce52367066d7c2971a7f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20family%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20relaxing%20by%20the%20pool.%3Cp%3EMary%20Kearl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20our%20toddler%20was%20napping%20or%20sleeping%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20able%20to%20take%20turns%20enjoying%20the%20pool%20or%20evening%20entertainment%20with%20our%20older%20daughter%20without%20having%20to%20do%20anything%20more%20than%20walk%20up%20a%20flight%20or%20two%20of%20stairs.%20While%20one%20of%20us%20was%20out%2C%20the%20other%20stayed%20in%20the%20nearby%20room%20and%20got%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20shows%20or%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWin%2C%20win%20%E2%80%94%20and%20another%20perk%20of%20a%20small%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1635746-afbf-46ab-a11a-ffcba39ebf0a%5C%22%3EAfter%20this%2C%20I'd%20definitely%20take%20another%20river%20cruise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22view%20from%20balcony%20of%20water%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efce52a98bc8fdc096f729%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI'm%20sold%20on%20river%20cruises.%3Cp%3EMary%20Kearl%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20our%20river%20cruise%20was%20just%20so%20beautiful%20and%20relaxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20traveled%20to%2030%20countries%20with%20my%20oldest%20daughter%20and%20nine%20with%20my%20youngest%2C%20and%20I%20can%20say%20from%20plenty%20of%20experience%20that%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-traveler-never-check-bag-carry-on-kids-packing-tips-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20with%20small%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20ever%20easy%20or%20restful%2C%20so%20being%20able%20to%20fit%20in%20moments%20of%20relaxation%20into%20this%20vacation%20was%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20look%20ahead%20to%20future%20travels%2C%20I%20would%20love%20to%20incorporate%20cruising%20into%20my%20family's%20adventures%2C%20particularly%20as%20a%20way%20to%20get%20one-of-a-kind%20views%20of%20places%20we've%20never%20been%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I'm%20still%20not%20sold%20on%20ocean%20cruises%2C%20I'd%20happily%20do%20a%20river%20sailing%20again%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20just%20to%20experience%20a%20new%20place%20by%20water%20while%20avoiding%20crowds%20and%20seasickness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Friver-cruise-with-family-what-its-like-worth-it-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777463881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69efce52a98bc8fdc096f728%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Friver-cruise-with-family-what-its-like-worth-it-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20first%20river%20cruise%20with%20my%20family%20wasn't%20what%20I%20expected%2C%20and%20it%20had%20many%20perks%20for%20my%20small%20kids.%20Here's%20what%20it's%20like%20and%20why%20we%20loved%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mary%20Kearl)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fed%20meeting%20updates%3A%20Will%20FOMC%20hold%20interest%20rates%3F%20What%20to%20expect%20from%20Jerome%20Powell's%20last%20meeting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jerome%20powell%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0c8b49244129ecb2f8c94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJerome%20Powell's%20term%20as%20central%20bank%20chair%20ends%20in%20May.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Park%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20fourth%20Fed%20day%20of%20the%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20set%20to%20be%20Jerome%20Powell's%20swan%20song.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Open%20Market%20Committee%20will%20announce%20its%20April%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-meeting-january-jerome-powell-interest-rates-key-takeaways-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest%20rate%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%202%20p.m.%20ET.%20Powell's%20term%20ends%20on%20May%2015%2C%20making%20this%20meeting%20his%20last%2C%20pending%20the%20confirmation%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-nominee-kevin-warsh-confirmation-hearing-takeaways-ai-fomc-independence-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKevin%20Warsh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Trump's%20nominee%20to%20be%20the%20next%20Fed%20chair.%20The%20meeting%20also%20comes%20amid%20a%20new%20development%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20probe%20into%20the%20Fed's%20construction%20efforts%20on%20its%20DC%20buildings%2C%20a%20continued%20stalemate%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20and%20ongoing%20inflation%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20will%20cover%20the%20news%20all%20day%2C%20including%20insights%20from%20economists%2C%20market%20analysts%2C%20and%20central%20bank%20leaders.%20Check%20back%20here%20for%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20job%20market%20looked%20brighter%20in%20March%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-report-march-data-live-updates-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejobs%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20showed%20stronger%20job%20creation%20in%20March%20after%20the%20previous%20report%20showed%20that%20weather%20and%20a%20healthcare%20strike%20affected%20employment%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20added%20178%2C000%20jobs%20in%20March%2C%20blowing%20past%20expectations%20and%20offsetting%20the%20133%2C000%20lost%20the%20month%20before.%20Healthcare%20and%20the%20leisure%20and%20hospitality%20sector%20had%20the%20largest%20gains%20among%20major%20industries.%20However%2C%20the%20Iran%20war%20could%20still%20have%20knock-on%20effects%20for%20the%20US%20economy%20down%20the%20line.%20Diane%20Swonk%2C%20KPMG's%20chief%20economist%2C%20said%20this%20doesn't%20reflect%20the%20full%20effects%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20shock%20to%20energy%20prices%20and%20supply%20chains%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20survey's%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20tells%20us%20that%20what%20we%20already%20knew%20was%20that%20we%20entered%20the%20year%20with%20the%20tailwind%2C%20part%20of%20it%20being%20the%20catch-up%20to%20the%20government%20shutdown%2C%20part%20of%20it%20being%20fiscal%20stimulus%2C%20but%20now%20we're%20facing%20the%20headwinds%20of%20much%20higher%20energy%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20Swonk%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20expect%20to%20see%20much%20softer%20job%20creation%20going%20forward%20as%20uncertainty%20has%20spiked%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22cust