nsider.com%2Fbusiness-immigration-lawyer-trump-clients-fear-visas-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echanging%20immigration%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharts-fed-chair-jerome-powell-jobs-inflation-interest-rates-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERead%20full%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMarkets%20ready%20for%20a%20busy%20day%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20the%20Fed%20decision%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-preview-key-numbers-alphabet-microsoft-amazon-meta-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20slew%20of%20Big%20Tech%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20set%20to%20be%20a%20busy%20day%20for%20markets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20major%20US%20indexes%20are%20set%20to%20open%20a%20little%20higher%2C%20with%20futures%20pointing%20to%20both%20the%20Dow%20and%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20gaining%20just%200.1%25%20at%20the%20open%2C%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20set%20to%20tick%200.4%25%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20in%20Europe%20are%20down%20on%20the%20day%2C%20though%20falls%20are%20largely%20limited.%20The%20biggest%20drop%20is%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20the%20FTSE%20100%20is%20down%20roughly%200.8%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20commodity%20markets%2C%20oil%20prices%20rose%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20seemingly%20spurred%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20latest%20threat%20to%20Iran.%20Early%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F116486959174837748%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20shared%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20an%20AI-generated%20image%20of%20himself%20wearing%20sunglasses%20and%20holding%20a%20gun%20with%20the%20caption%20%26quot%3BNo%20more%20Mr.%20Nice%20Guy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20before%207%20a.m.%20ET%2C%20Brent%20crude%2C%20the%20international%20benchmark%2C%20was%202.8%25%20higher%20at%20%24107.30%20per%20barrel%2C%20while%20WTI%20crude%20was%20up%203.3%25%20to%20%24103.25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20near-guaranteed%20hold%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20CME%20FedWatch%20%E2%80%94%20which%20estimates%20probabilities%20of%20the%20Fed's%20choices%20based%20on%20market%20moves%20%E2%80%94%20is%20predicting%20a%20100%25%20chance%20of%20a%20rate%20hold.%20The%20FOMC%20aims%20to%20balance%20both%20sides%20of%20its%20dual%20mandate%2C%20fostering%20stable%20prices%20and%20maximum%20employment.%20Lowering%20rates%20could%20help%20thaw%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-market-gains-losses-back-forth-immigration-aging-labor-force-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrozen%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20carries%20the%20risk%20of%20rising%20inflation.%20It's%20likely%20the%20Fed%20will%20take%20a%20moderately%20restrictive%20stance%2C%20keeping%20rates%20steady%20alongside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-rise-iran-war-peace-talks-strait-hormuz-shipping-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoil%20shocks%20from%20the%20Iran%20war%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20end%20of%20an%20era%20(most%20likely)%3Cp%3EAfter%20holding%20the%20post%20since%202018%2C%20Wednesday%20is%20set%20to%20be%20Powell's%20last%20meeting%20as%20central%20bank%20chair.%20His%20term%20is%20officially%20up%20on%20May%2015%2C%20and%20Trump%20nominee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-drops-probe-against-fed-chair-powell-warsh-confirmation-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWarsh%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20greenlit%20by%20the%20Senate%20as%20successor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Senate%20Banking%20Committee%20is%20scheduled%20to%20meet%20this%20morning%20to%20vote%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20advance%20his%20confirmation%20to%20the%20full%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20rare%20for%20a%20chair%20to%20remain%20on%20the%20Federal%20Open%20Market%20Committee%20after%20their%20tenure%2C%20but%20Powell%20has%20hinted%20that%20he%20may%20hold%20on%20to%20his%20governor%20seat%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20make%20that%20decision%20based%20on%20what%20I%20think%20is%20best%20for%20the%20institution%20and%20for%20the%20people%20we%20serve%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20last%20month.%20Powell%20is%20eligible%20to%20vote%20on%20the%20committee%20until%202028%2C%20if%20he%20were%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-meeting-interest-rates-fomc-jerome-powell-april-live-updates-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777463734000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0c99229fef86fd43d37a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-meeting-interest-rates-fomc-jerome-powell-april-live-updates-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Federal%20Reserve%20will%20announce%20its%20interest%20rate%20decision%20at%20its%20April%20meeting%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20Fed%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell's%20last.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Madison%20Hoff%2CAllie%20Kelly%2CWill%20Martin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20discounts%20to%20Dior%3A%20What's%20driving%20premium%20pivot%20in%20fashion%20ecommerce%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777463632000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-04%2F29%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F1200X628%2F1777462158-3694.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-fashion-ecommerce-premiumisation-luxury-shift-myntra-nyka-tata-cliq-126042901007_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20fashion%20ecommerce%20players%20are%20increasi