ime%20it%20gained%20a%20follower%2C%20Emy%2C%20a%20custom-made%20green-and-yellow%20plush%20toy%2C%20would%20move%201%20millimeter%20closer%20to%20being%20thrown%20from%20the%20world's%20tallest%20building%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20account%20quickly%20attracted%20thousands%20of%20followers%2C%20likes%2C%20and%20comments%2C%20and%20was%20thrown%C2%A0from%20830%2C000mm%2C%20the%20equivalent%20height%C2%A0to%20the%20Burj%20Khalifa%2C%20in%20February.%20The%20stakes%20were%20raised%20again%3A%20in%C2%A0March%2C%20Emy%20was%20thrown%20from%20a%20high-altitude%20balloon%2C%20116%2C419%20feet%20above%20Kingston%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmy's%20co-creator%2C%20Sachin%20Raoul%20%E2%80%94%20a%2033-year-old%20tech%20founder%20and%20entrepreneur%20who%20was%20included%20in%20Forbes'%2030%20under%2030%20in%202022%20%E2%80%94%20is%20insistent%20that%20this%20is%20not%20another%20example%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrain-rot-summer-coldplaygate-jet2holidays-monoculture-movies-songs-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20%26quot%3Bbrain%20rot%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaoul%20wants%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20encourage%20people%20to%20step%20away%20from%20their%20screens%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20caveat%20that%20you%20need%20a%20phone%20and%20an%20Instagram%20account%20to%20engage%20with%20Emy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20into%20the%20real%20world%2C%20inspired%20by%20Emy's%20adventures%20in%20the%20great%20outdoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20page%20also%20invites%20followers%20to%20take%20part%20in%20in-person%20challenges%20%E2%80%94%20finding%20a%20mini%20version%20of%20the%20Emy%20toy%20out%20in%20the%20wild%2C%20for%20example%2C%20in%20the%20style%20of%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20Go%3Cs%3E.%3C%2Fs%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20da