l.%20%26quot%3BThat%20made%20me%20reflect%20on%20the%20work%20I%20was%20doing%20every%20day%2C%20and%20that's%20really%20what%20pushed%20me%20to%20do%20something%20completely%20different%20and%20create%20something%20that%20was%20inspiring%20for%20young%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChasing%20adventure%20and%20love%20are%20the%20two%20most%20important%20values%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%20%26quot%3BThere%20isn't%20much%20adventure%20around%20building%20apps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaoul%20said%20at%20this%20point%2C%20Emy%20doesn't%20generate%20any%20revenue%2C%20but%20the%20long-term%20plan%20is%20to%20bring%20in%20sponsorships%20and%20collaborations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Raoul%20poses%20while%20wearing%20a%20checked%20yellow%2C%20green%20and%20blue%20jacket%20and%20top.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69eb3c2d367066d7c29707ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESachin%20Raoul%20is%20the%20brains%20behind%20Emy%20Adventure.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sachin%20Raoul%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERaoul%20and%20a%20friend%20had%20decided%20to%20experiment%20with%20weird%20and%20creative%20projects%2C%20trialing%20low-cost%20ideas%20to%20see%20what%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-capitalize-on-going-viral-grow-sustainable-small-business-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egain%20traction%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concept%20of%20dropping%20a%20plushie%20from%20a%20height%20tied%20to%20our%20follower%20count%20was%20the%20one%20that%20broke%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20Raoul%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20custom%20plush%20toy%20we%20now%20know%20as%20Emy%20was%20originally%20an%20avatar.%20Raoul%20had%20previously%20created%20an%20AI%20pet%20companion%20app%20for%20young%20people%20and%20therefore%20owned%20the%20intellectual%20property%20rights%20to%20the%20Emy%20avatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20then%20redesigned%20into%20a%20custom%20plush%20toy%20so%20it%20could%20be%20used%20for%20social%20media%20content.%20They%20have%20since%20shut%20down%20the%20app%20to%20focus%20on%20Emy%20Adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a683f7f-b91f-4b3f-b713-ea024ffb6034%5C%22%3EAbsurd%20and%20curious%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20younger%20generations%20are%20especially%20enthusiastic%20about%20Emy%2C%20Raoul%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Navarra%2C%20a%20social%20media%20consultant%2C%20said%20it's%20likely%20because%20of%20the%20simplicity%20and%20absurdity%20of%20the%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20millennial%20social%20media%20was%20about%20connection%2C%20Gen%20Z%2C%20Gen%20Alpha%20social%20media%20is%20about%20curiosity%20and%20immediacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Navarra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20busy%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-top-kick-livestreamer-n3on-turns-controversy-into-clippable-fame-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echaotic%20social%20media%20feed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20simple%20format%20of%C2%A0posts%20has%20also%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20younger%20audiences%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20there's%20the%20participatory%20aspect%20of%20it%20that%20appeals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGen%20Z%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpocket-watch-launches-new-teen-shows-hulu-tubi-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGen%20Alpha%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20just%20consume%20content%20nowadays.%20They%20expect%20to%20be%20able%20to%20interact%20with%20it%2C%20or%20influence%20it%2C%20and%20remix%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%