%20his%20meme%20that%20joked%20about%20how%20quickly%20the%20account%20was%20gaining%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20making%20memes%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20so%20it%20was%20something%20that%20really%20resonated%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Lander%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELander%20initially%20followed%20the%20account%20because%20it%20seemed%20catchy%20and%20engaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raoul%20Sachin%20and%20friend%20hold%20plush%20toy%20Emy%20on%20top%20of%20the%20peak%20of%20a%20mountain.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69eb3a89367066d7c29707a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERaoul%2C%20pictured%20here%20(L)%2C%20has%20filmed%20Emy%20content%20in%20the%20French%20Alps.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sachin%20Raoul%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERaoul%20said%20this%20level%20of%20engagement%20is%20exactly%20what%20they%20had%20hoped%20for%20with%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Emy's%20purpose%20is%20to%20inspire%20people%20to%20go%20out%20into%20the%20real%20world%2C%20Raoul%20believes%20people%20are%20resistant%20to%20being%20told%20to%20put%20their%20phones%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20does%20work%20is%20meeting%20people%20where%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20use%20the%20medium%20they're%20already%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20i.e.%2C%20phones%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20show%20them%20what%20they're%20missing%2C%26quot%3B%20Raoul%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20give%20them%20a%20glimpse%20of%20a%20helicopter%20drop%20over%20Alaska%2C%20or%20a%20plushie%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20world's%20tallest%20building%2C%20and%20you%20let%20the%20content%20do%20the%20talking%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femy-adventure-weird-plush-toy-winning-the-i