3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMrBeast%20is%20coming%20to%20Madison%20Avenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber's%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-builds-management-team-with-hires-from-tiktok-snapchat-nbcu-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBeast%20Industries%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20a%20VP%20of%20agency%20partnerships%2C%20CMO%20Insider%20can%20exclusively%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20person%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20serving%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bprimary%20bridge%20between%20the%20MrBeast%20ecosystem%20and%20major%20agency%20holding%20companies%20(WPP%2C%20Publicis%2C%20Omnicom%2C%20IPG%2C%20Havas%2C%20Dentsu)%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20job%20posting.%20(Perhaps%20this%20person%20could%20also%20flag%20that%20IPG%20is%20no%20more%20after%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomnicom-ceo-john-wren-ipg-merger-ai-job-cuts-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emerger%20with%20Omnicom%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMrBeast%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Jimmy%20Donaldson%2C%20is%20the%20world's%20most-followed%20YouTuber%2C%20and%20Beast%20Industries%20encompasses%20a%20range%20of%20properties%2C%20including%20Amazon%20Prime%20Video's%20%26quot%3BBeast%20Games%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20snack%20company%20Feastables.%20Beast%20Industries%20has%20secured%20brand%20partnerships%20with%20Salesforce%2C%20Starbucks%2C%20Lowe's%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20been%20beefing%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-jimmy-donaldson-youtube-seeks-cmo-to-build-entertainment-giant-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eits%20exec%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20hires%20from%20major%20media%20companies%20like%20TikTok%20and%20NBCUniversal.%20(It's%20also%20branching%20out%20into%20new%20areas%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-plots-move-into-ai-native-entertainment-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20native%20entertainment%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20listing%20for%20the%20VP%20of%20agency%20partnerships%20role%20says%20Beast%20Industries%20is%20looking%20for%20someone%20with%20experience%20in%20negotiating%20%26quot%3Bhigh-value%2C%20multi-year%20master%20service%20agreements%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20contracts%20that%20define%20longer-term%20relationships%20between%20agencies%20and%20ad%20sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20important%20development%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20MrBeast's%20ad%20business%20as%20his%20company%20looks%20to%20translate%20its%20reach%20into%20something%20agencies%20can%20buy%20predictably%20and%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStefan%20Bardega%2C%20formerly%20an%20exec%20at%20the%20Dentsu%20agency%20iProspect%20and%20now%20at%20the%20communications%20agency%20IDX%2C%20said%20that%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20ad%20spend%20is%20still%20deployed%20through%20the%20major%20ad%20holding%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20creators%20want%20to%20go%20direct%20to%20big%20brands%2C%20they%20find%20procurement%2C%20measurement%20frameworks%2C%20and%20risk%20controls%20usually%20route%20budgets%20back%20through%20these%20global%20agency%20structures%2C%26quot%3B%20Bardega%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20IDX's%20head%20of%20performance%20marketing%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20companies%20like%20Beast%20Industries%2C%20which%20are%20hoping%20to%20secure%20contracts%20with%20major%20holding%20companies%2C%20need%20to%20maintain%20predictable%20pricing%20and%20adhere%20to%20industry%20standards%20in%20areas%20like%20ad%20measurement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20to%20be%20easy%20to%20buy%2C%20not%20just%20strategically%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Bardega%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-wants-to-go-deeper-with-ad-agencies-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusines