ans%20scroll%20their%20phones%20during%20commercial%20breaks%2C%20skip%20ads%20on%20YouTube%2C%20or%20block%20ads%20altogether%2C%20marketers%20need%20to%20get%20creative%20about%20maximizing%20the%20value%20of%20their%20big%20sponsorship%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Kraft%20Heinz%2C%20that%20means%20focusing%20on%20what%20Kaplan%20describes%20as%20%26quot%3Bmarketing%20that%20happens%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20type%20of%20content%20that's%20designed%20to%20be%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20Oscar%20Mayer%20brand%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20its%20second%20%26quot%3BWienie%20500%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20a%20fleet%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foscar-mayer-says-goodbye-historic-weinermobile-new-frankmobile-hot-dogs-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehot-dog-shaped%20Wienermobiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20race%20around%20the%20Indianapolis%20Motor%20Speedway%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findycar-pit-crew-training-racing-fitness-andretti-autosport-indianapolis-500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Indy%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20weekend%20in%20May.%20Last%20year's%20event%20was%20watched%20live%20by%208%20million%20viewers%20online%20and%20drew%2085%2C000%20fans%20in%20person%2C%20Kraft%20Heinz%20said.%20The%20company%20said%20the%20race%20helped%20it%20sell%20half%20a%20million%20Oscar%20Mayer%20Wieners%20during%20Memorial%20Day%2C%20a%20four-year%20sales%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20first%20Wienie%20500%2C%20Oscar%20Mayer%20might%20have%20run%20an%20ad%20campaign%20and%20some%20trade%20marketing%20programs%20around%20Memorial%20Day%20weekend%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20moments%20on%20the%20calendar%20for%20hot%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20it%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Btentpole%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20marketers%2C%20sports%20offer%20some%20of%20the%20last%20remaining%20mass-reach%20vehicles%20in%20media.%20Sponsorships%20can%20also%20impact%20consumer%20perception%20of%20brands.%20An%20analysis%20by%20the%20research%20company%20Nielsen%20of%20100%20sports%20partnerships%20between%202020%20and%202021%20found%20that%20sponsorships%20drove%20an%20average%2010%25%20lift%20in%20purchase%20intent%20%E2%80%94%20consumers'%20likelihood%20to%20buy%20a%20product%20or%20service%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20fans%20exposed%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22295d3c90-558b-42b2-afce-8eddf11bc048%5C%22%3EKraft%20Heinz%20has%20a%20%24600%20million%20turnaround%20plan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKaplan's%20rejuvenated%20sports%20sponsorship%20approach%20is%20one%20element%20of%20a%20larger%20%24600%20million%20investment%20by%20Kraft%20Heinz%20in%20marketing%2C%20research%2C%20and%20other%20sales%20approaches%20to%20strengthen%20its%20brands%20and%20turn%20around%20sales%20declines%2C%20particularly%20in%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20confront%20changing%20consumer%20tastes%20around%20processed%20food%20and%20pressure%20on%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Kraft%20Heinz%20paused%20a%20plan%20to%20separate%20its%20sauces%2C%20seasonings%2C%20and%20spreads%20division%20and%20its%20grocery%20store%20staples%20unit%20into%20two%20independent%20companies.%20Its%20stock%20has%20been%20lingering%20at%20six-year%20lows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20Kraft%20Heinz%20announced%20the%20pause%2C%20its%20new%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkelloggs-is-breaking-up-business-cereal-plant-snack-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESteve%20Cahillane%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20previous%20cost-cutting%20had%20gone%20too%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20that%20we%20have%20historically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkraft-heinz-cut-expenses-too-deeply-private-equity-owner-ceo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunderinvested%20in%20our%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20the%20business%2C%20resulting%20in%20persistent%20share%20loss%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20Cahillane%20said%20on%20the%20company's%20February%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%2C%20Kaplan%20said%20he's%20been%20working%20to%20eliminate%20formalities%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20back-and-forth%20of%20briefings%20and%20presentation%20meetings%20with%20its%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20to%20the%20nugget%20of%20the%20best%20ideas%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20one%20of%20these%20brainstorming%20sessions%20that%20the%20Wienie%20500%20idea%20came%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaplan%20said%20it%20required%20putting%20in%20the%20early%20work%20to%20ensure%20everyone%2C%20from%20legal%20to%20the%20brand%20teams%20and%20the%20media%20team%2C%20was%20all%20talking%20from%20the%20same%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaplan%20has%20codified%20the%20process%20internally%20under%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bcollaborativity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20best%20ideas%20that%20have%20happened%20over%20time%20build%20on%20a%20text%20message%20or%20group%20chat%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said.%20%26quot%3BCreativity%20is%20iterative%20as%20a%20process%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20it%20can%20be%20messy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkraft-heinz-cmo-revamped-sponsorship-strategy-around-memorable-stunts-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777462801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0c68f9244129ecb2f8c77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkraft-heinz-cmo-revamped-sponsorship-strategy-around-memorable-stunts-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kraft%20Heinz%20North%20America%20CMO%20Todd%20Kaplan%20lifted%20the%20lid%20on%20why%20he's%20ditching%20simple%20%26quot%3Blogo%20slaps%26quot%3B%20for%20cont