-y-o-y-to-rs-4-271-crore-126042900953_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20think%20magazines%20are%20the%20new%20vinyl.%20I%20opened%20a%20magazine%20shop%20in%20Maine%20to%20prove%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stacy%20Mitchell%20headshot%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1e6b19244129ecb2f9315%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStacy%20Mitchell%20opened%20a%20magazine%20shop%20in%20Portland%2C%20Maine.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stacy%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStacy%20Mitchell%20is%20a%2036-year-old%20in%20Portland%2C%20Maine%2C%20who%20has%20always%20loved%20magazines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202025%2C%20she%20opened%20a%20magazine%20shop%2C%20hopeful%20that%20she'd%20be%20able%20to%20pass%20on%20her%20love%20of%20magazines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20have%20been%20either%20very%20excited%20about%20the%20opportunity%20to%20buy%20magazines%20or%20confused.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Stacy%20Mitchell%2C%20owner%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fboldmags.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBold%20Magazine%20Shop%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-moved-china-from-us-compares-culture-america-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisited%20Beijing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20started%20a%20new%20tradition%3A%20buying%20a%20Vogue%20magazine%20from%20each%20country%20I%20traveled%20through.%20The%20Chinese%20Vogue%20was%20beautiful%2C%20emblematic%20of%20the%20place%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMagazines%20have%20this%20way%20of%20transporting%20and%20engaging%20you%20in%20a%20way%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-11-most-massively-popular-magazines-youve-never-heard-of-2012-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eonline%20magazines%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20can't%20do.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20totally%20present%20to%20take%20in%20a%20magazine%2C%20to%20understand%20how%20it's%20curated%2C%20and%20to%20appreciate%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20art%20and%20words%20within.%20Often%2C%20reading%20a%20magazine%20sparks%20an%20idea%20I%20pursue%20further.%20All%20of%20this%20involves%20time%20and%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20magazines%20aren't%20read%20like%20they%20used%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296a6e157-76ad-4f79-aa61-eb6a05f36c5c%5C%22%3EI%20saw%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20magazines%20outside%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20on%20to%20buy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchloe-malle-anna-wintour-new-vogue-editor-in-chief-parents-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVogue%20magazines%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20noticing%20that%20other%20countries%20seemed%20to%20have%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20magazines%20than%20I%20saw%20in%20the%20US.%20While%20New%20York%20City%20had%20plenty%20of%20places%20to%20buy%20niche%20magazines%2C%20there%20weren't%20many%20other%20towns%20and%20cities%20where%20I%20could%20access%20the%20magazines%20I'd%20seen%20during%20my%20travels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20got%20me%20thinking%20and%20dreaming%20about%20owning%20my%20own%20magazine%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stacy%20Mitchell%20at%20her%20shop%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1e84e29fef86fd43d3e7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222320%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStacy%20Mitchell%20feels%20like%20magazines%20will%20have%20a%20comeback%20like%20vinyl%20did.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Georgia%20Dixon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsand-island-scott-kern-maine-summer-life-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECity%20of%20Portland%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20an%20open%20call%20for%20small%20businesses%20to%20pitch%20to%20set%20up%20a%20shop%20in%20a%20gazebo%20right%20by%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20started%20making%20actual%20plans%20for%20a%20store%20that%20sold%20magazines%2C%20planning%20how%20it%20would%20work%2C%20where%20I%20would%20get%20magazines%2C%20and%20how%20I%20would%20generate%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20while%20I%20continued%20working%20my%20job%2C%20I%20researched%20endlessly%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20I%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-a-business-according-to-successful-entrepreneurs-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emake%20my%20dream%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20get%20the%20gazebo%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20catalyst%20I%20needed.%20I%20started%20looking%20for%20retail%20spaces%20and%20found%20an%20affordable%20building%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20needed%20some%20fixing%20up%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20center%20of%20Portland's%20arts%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22072d4355-3999-4243-bf72-c9f0f189783a%5C%22%3EI%20opened%20a%20magazine%20shop%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202025%2C%20I%20started%20leasing%20the%20space%2C%20and%20in%20November%202025%2C%20I%20opened%20my%20doors%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20my%20shop%2C%20there%20are%20175%20titles%20to%20choose%20from%20(and%20this%20number%20continues%20to%20grow)%2C%20all%20neatly%20and%20minimalistically%20arranged%20by%20category%20on%20the%20walls%20and%20atop%20tables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224426%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bold%20magazine%20shop%20front%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1e8793b4f7c3af2b7afb3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223320%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBold%20opened%20in%20November%202025.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stacy%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20loved%20watching%20people%20come%20in%20to%20browse%2C%20deciding%20which%20magazine%20to%20purchase%20and%20take%20home%20or%20to%20the%20coffee%20shop%20next%20door%20to%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20experience%20has%20been%20a%20learning%20curve.%20I've%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20buy%20from%20publishers%20and%20distributors%20around%20the%20world%2C%20which%20magazines%20to%20buy%20and%20how%20many%20of%20each%20to%20sell%2C%20and%20how%20to%20stay%20afloat%20in%20January%20and%20February%2C%20the%20slowest%20months%20for%20retail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20all%20been%20worth%20it%2C%20especially%20after%20hearing%20people's%20responses%20%E2%80%94%20either%20excitement%20that%20a%20magazine%20retailer%20has%20finally%20come%20to%20Portland%2C%20or%20surprise%20that%20I'd%20choose%20to%20open%20a%20magazine%20shop%20in%20this%20online-reading%20era.%20All%20of%20the%20responses%20spark%20conversation%20about%20magazines%2C%20which%20can%20only%20be%20a%20good%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20really%20busy%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20Christmas%2C%20but%20it%20has%20been%20quieter%20in%20January%20and%20February.%20As%20the%20weather%20brightens%2C%20I'm%20expecting%20more%20and%20more%20people%20to%20walk%20through%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20rule%20I've%20made%20for%20the%20shop%20is%20that%20magazines%20must%20be%20really%2C%20really%20good%20and%20the%20most%20recent%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20successful%20titles%20have%20been%20Pencil%2C%20Fukt%2C%20and%20Never%20Too%20Small%2C%20an%20Australian%20small-interiors%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226955d30f-9570-48f8-81cf-00ec4e77ab72%5C%22%3EPeople%20are%20excited%20about%20physical%20magazines%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%20little%20girl%20came%20in%20and%20bought%20a%20magazine.%20Only%20after%20she%20left%20did%20I%20realize%20that%20my%20magazine%20shop%20might%20have%20ignited%20her%20love%20of%20magazines.%20My%20shop%20can%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20when%20I%20opened%20the%20shop%2C%20a%20woman%20waited%20expectantly%20outside%20for%20me%20to%20let%20her%20in%2C%20so%20excited%20that%20this%20type%20of%20shop%20now%20existed.%20Magazines%20had%20previously%20been%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20her%20life%2C%20and%20she%20couldn't%20access%20them%20like%20she%20once%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20excited%20about%20what%20the%20magazine%20shop%20will%20do%20for%20others%20and%20how%20it%20will%20inspire%20others%20to%20become%20magazine%20readers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20this%20feeling%20that%20magazines%20will%20become%20the%20new%20vinyl%20record.%20I%20think%20they'll%20make%20a%20comeback%2C%20and%20I'm%20ready%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopened-magazine-shop-digital-age-portland-print-comeback-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777461672000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1e6b19244129ecb2f9315%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopened-magazine-shop-digital-age-portland-print-comeback-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stacy%20Mitchell%20opened%20a%20magazine%20shop%20in%20Portland%2C%20Maine%2C%20betting%20on%20print%20in%20a%20digital%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20seeing%20growing%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Crosby%20Medlicott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Bada%20shauk%20hai%20trekking%20ka%E2%80%99%3A%20Two%20sisters%20aged%20over%2070%20on%20Kedarnath%20trek%20win%20hearts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777461489000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130605334%2Cimgsize-153690.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.i