-for-chinese-made-suv-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efactory%20in%20South%20Carolina%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamuelsson%20cautioned%20that%20any%20discussions%20would%20be%20dependent%20on%20Geely%20successfully%20navigating%20the%20daunting%20regulatory%20environment%20for%20Chinese%20vehicles%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAssuming%20that%2C%20of%20course%2C%20we%20could%20discuss%20building%20cars%20in%20the%20plant%2C%20as%20we%20have%20capacity%2C%26quot%3B%20Samuelsson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese-developed%20vehicle%20software%20and%20hardware%20are%20effectively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-proposes-ban-china-russia-tech-connected-cars-security-fears-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebanned%20from%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20rules%20introduced%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeely%2C%20BYD%2C%20and%20China's%20other%20EV%20powerhouses%20are%20taking%20market%20share%20from%20Western%20automakers%20in%20China%20and%20Europe%20by%20offering%20a%20variety%20of%20affordable%2C%20high-tech%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeely's%20sales%20have%20grown%20rapidly%20in%20recent%20years%20on%20the%20back%20of%20cut-priced%20EVs%20like%20its%20Galaxy%20hatchback%2C%20which%20starts%20at%2068%2C800%20yuan%20(%249%2C670)%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20companies%20have%20been%20effectively%20blocked%20from%20selling%20their%20cars%20in%20the%20US%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-electric-car-get-ready-to-pay-250-percent-tariff-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etariffs%20of%20over%20100%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeely%20executives%20said%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20China's%20second-largest%20automaker%2C%20which%20also%20owns%20Western%20brands%20Polestar%20and%20Volvo%2C%20could%20announce%20plans%20to%20expand%20into%20the%20US%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felectrek.co%2F2026%2F01%2F05%2Fchinese-auto-giant-geely-to-announce-entry-into-us-ev-market-within-2-3-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enext%20two%20to%20three%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20its%20vehicles%20at%20Volvo's%20plant%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20could%20be%20one%20way%20of%20circumventing%20the%20sky-high%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20vehicles%2C%20although%20the%20restrictions%20on%20Chinese%20hardware%20and%20software%20would%20still%20be%20a%20major%20barrier.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20factory%20currently%20produces%20Volvo's%20EX90%20SUV%20and%20the%20Polestar%203%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20that%20Geely%20had%20also%20held%20talks%20with%20Ford%20about%20a%20potential%20partnership%20in%20the%20US%20that%20could%20include%20the%20Chinese%20company%20licensing%20its%20technology%20to%20the%20Detroit%20auto%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20attempt%20to%20bring%20Chinese%20EVs%20to%20the%20US%20would%20likely%20face%20renewed%20political%20opposition%2C%20with%20US%20auto%20executives%20warning%20that%20a%20wave%20of%20cheap%20Chinese%20vehicles%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ceo-jim-farley-chinese-carmakers-entering-us-devastating-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edevastating%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublican%20Senator%20Bernie%20Moreno%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos-transportation%2Frepublican-senator-proposes-widen-us-ban-chinese-autos-2026-03-31%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposed%20a%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20ban%20Chinese%20cars%20from%20US%20roads%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamuelsson%20said%20that%20European%20and%20American%20automakers%20would%20come%20under%20severe%20pressure%20from%20insurgent%20Chinese%20EV%20makers%20as%20they%20expand%20beyond%20their%20home%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Volvo%20CEO%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20had%20recently%20test-driven%20cars%20from%20Chinese%20brands%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ceo-jim-farley-xiaomi-tesla-chinese-ev-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EXiaomi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Zeekr%2C%20and%20had%20been%20impressed%20by%20their%20advanced%20tech%20and%20premium%20feel.%20Samuelsson%20added%20that%20Western%20companies%20will%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20help%26quot%3B%20and%20learn%20from%20their%20Chinese%20rivals%20if%20they%20are%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20cost%20of%20building%20EVs%20and%20compete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20a%20huge%20competition%20pressure%20on%20the%20old%20industry%20from%20the%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamuelsson%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20following%20Volvo's%20first-quarter%20earnings%2C%20in%20which%20it%20reported%20declining%20revenue%20and%20profits%20as%20the%20Swedish%20automaker%20faces%20slowing%20EV%20sales%20in%20the%20US%20and%20fierce%20competition%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvolvo-build-chinese-evs-america-ceo-geely-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777458324000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1cf269244129ecb2f92c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvolvo-build-chinese-evs-america-ceo-geely-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22H%C3%A5kan%20Samuelsson%20told%20BI%20that%20Volvo%20would%20consider%20building%20cars%20from%20its%20Chinese%20parent%20company%2C%20Geely%2C%20at%20its%20factory%20in%20South%20Carolina.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20stopped%20giving%20my%20kids%20big%20birthday%20gifts.%20Now%2C%20I%20take%20them%20on%20one-on-one%20trips%20instead.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20daughter%20stands%20along%20the%20shoreline%20while%20on%20a%20mother-daughter%20trip.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea5321367066d7c29702ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221134%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20taking%20her%20children%20on%20solo%20trips%20gives%20her%20a%20chance%20to%20bond%20with%20each%20of%20them%20one-on-one.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sandra%20Lee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20my%20daughter%20turned%209%2C%20I%20booked%20a%20sleepover%20for%20the%20two%20of%20us%20at%20a%20museum.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20take%20each%20of%20my%20kids%20on%20a%20trip%20for%20their%20birthday%2C%20without%20their%20sibling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20love%20the%20chance%20to%20connect%20with%20my%20kids%20on%20these%20unique%20getaways.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20we%20did%20this%20every%20day%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20my%20son%20as%20we%20played%20a%20game%20of%20UNO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-resorts-for-kids-families-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20swim%20in%20the%20pool%2C%20both%20of%20us%20still%20riding%20an%20ice%20cream-fueled%20high.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20were%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspend-birthdays-solo-trips-better-celebration-30s-40s-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eannual%20birthday%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20just%20like%20usual%2C%20it%20was%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us.%20This%20year%2C%20I%20planned%20an%20ice%20cream%20tour%20scavenger%20hunt%20across%20six%20shops%2C%20all%20in%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20parent%20of%20two%2C%20uninterrupted%20one-on-one%20time%20is%20rare.%20Between%20school%20schedules%2C%20activities%2C%20and%20the%20evening%20circus%20of%20family%20life%20with%20kids%2C%20most%20days%20are%20spent%20multitasking%2C%20not%20connecting.%20These%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgave-kids-trips-instead-of-presents-for-their-birthdays-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshort%20birthday%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20become%20my%20way%20of%20stepping%20outside%20that%20routine%20and%20reconnecting%20with%20each%20child%20individually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20not%20extravagant%20and%20only%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20away%20from%20home%2C%20but%20they've%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fannual-family-reunion-kids-impact-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emeaningful%20traditions%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewe%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219957276-64dc-455a-b4d2-178c26a672dc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20magic%20of%20the%20one-on-one%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tradition%20started%20when%20my%20daughter%20turned%209.%20Instead%20of%20a%20physical%20gift%2C%20I%20booked%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubmarine-airbnb-photos-world-war-ii-museum-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emuseum%20sleepover%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20realized%20how%20much%20the%20sibling%20dynamic%2C%20the%20usual%20competition%20for%20attention%2C%20goes%20away%20when%20a%20child%20is%20one-on-one%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20explored%20the%20museum%20together%2C%20shared%20cookies%20and%20milk%2C%20and%20fell%20asleep%20watching%20fish%20swim%20through%20the%20coral%20reef%20exhibit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222142%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20authors%20daughter%20looks%20into%20an%20aquarium.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea54ac367066d7c29702fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221607%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20one%20of%20the%20trips%2C%20the%20author%20and%20her%20daughter%20stayed%20overnight%20at%20a%20museuem.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sandra%20Lee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20kids%20have%20gotten%20older%2C%20these%20trips%20have%20become%20even%20more%20important%2C%20especially%20as%20they%20move%20into%20the%20tween%20and%20teen%20years.%20Being%20away%20from%20our%20usual%20routine%20creates%20space%20for%20the%20bigger%20conversations%2C%20the%20ones%20that%20don't%20happen%20in%20the%20car%20or%20at%20the%20dinner%20table.%20I%20think%20of%20it%20as%20an%20emotional%20bank%20account.%20Those%2048%20hours%20help%20sustain%20our%20relationship%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20bring%20back%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fput-an-end-to-cheap-souvenirs-traveling-with-kids-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20terms%20of%20things%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20we%20do%20bring%20back%20inside%20jokes%20and%20a%20stronger%20connection.%20Instead%20of%20just%20going%20through%20the%20motions%20of%20daily%20life%2C%20we're%20able%20to%20slow%20down%2C%20connect%2C%20and%20create%20moments%20that%20actually%20stick.%20At%2011%20and%209%2C%20my%20kids%20are%20at%20an%20age%20where%20these%20experiences%20carry%20more%20meaning%20and%20leave%20a%20lasting%20impression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272a5691f-805a-4e69-84ba-f329d9950f4e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20make%20sure%20the%20trips%20are%20simple%2C%20but%20meaningful%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20parents%20on%20social%20media%20taking%20their%20kids%20to%20Iceland%20or%20France%20for%20birthdays.%20That's%20not%20my%20reality.%20Instead%2C%20I%20stick%20close%20to%20home%2C%20but%20try%20to%20make%20the%20trip%20extra%20special%20by%20looking%20for%20unique%20themes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221205%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20child%20checks%20off%20ice%20cream%20flavors%20on%20a%20list.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea53b63fecbb42897a3443%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20used%20ChatGPT%20to%20create%20a%20passport%20for%20her%20son%20to%20check%20off%20various%20finds%20while%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20ice%20cream%20shops.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sandra%20Lee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20started%20turning%20to%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20plan%20the%20trip.%20For%20my%20son's%20ice%20cream%20tour%2C%20it%20designed%20a%20passport%20for%20us%20to%20check%20off%20flavors%20at%20every%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20try%20to%20tap%20into%20each%20child's%20unique%20interests.%20For%20my%20daughter's%20birthday%2C%20we%20went%20to%20San%20Francisco's%20Japantown.%20We%20shopped%20at%20Daiso%2C%20ate%20sushi%20delivered%20by%20a%20bullet%20train%2C%20and%20shared%20taiyaki%20ice%20cream.%20A%20fan%20of%20all%20things%20anime%20and%20Pokemon%2C%20this%20was%20one%20of%20our%20favorite%20trips%20and%20one%20we%20keep%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222856%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mom%20and%20child%20play%20Uno%20on%20a%20hotel%20bed.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea541c367066d7c29702f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222142%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20a%20hotel%20stay%20is%20a%20must%20to%20make%20these%20trips%20feel%20special.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sandra%20Lee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20save%20money%2C%20I%20book%20mid-week%20hotels%20during%20school%20breaks%20when%20rates%20are%20lower.%20The%20hotel%20stay%20is%20a%20requirement%2C%20though.%20It%20makes%20the%20time%20away%20feel%20like%20an%20actual%20trip%20rather%20than%20an%20outing%2C%20and%20being%20away%20from%20home%20allows%20me%20to%20be%20fully%20present%20so%20I%20can%20connect%20with%20my%20kid%20one-on-one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.c