e%20%26quot%3Bretribution%26quot%3B%20campaign.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1195829fef86fd43d3be1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20chart%20shows%20the%20damages%20actor%20Blake%20Lively%20says%20her%20hair-care%20and%20beverage%20businesses%20suffered%20after%20Justin%20Baldoni's%20online%20%26quot%3Bretribution%26quot%3B%20campaign.%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Court%20in%20Manhattan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20negative%20%26quot%3Bcampaign%26quot%3B%20quickly%20damaged%20a%20decadeslong%20acting%20career%20and%20upended%20a%20hair-care%20line%20launch%20that%20had%20been%20seven%20years%20in%20the%20planning%2C%20said%20Rim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20here%20an%20actress%20with%20a%20twenty-year%20track%20record%20of%20starring%20in%20major%20productions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BGossip%20Girl%26quot%3B%20star%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20biggest%20hair-care%20launch%20in%20Target%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Rim%20also%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Blake%20Brown%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20a%20matter%20of%20days%2C%20all%20that%20investment%20was%20erased%20due%20to%20this%20conduct%2C%26quot%3B%20Rim%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fighting%20to%20keep%20Lively's%20experts%20from%20testifying%2C%20Baldoni's%20side%20is%20arguing%20that%20the%20negative%20online%20comments%20and%20any%20losses%20she%20suffered%20in%20her%20career%20and%20business%20earnings%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20their%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20the%20kind%20of%20earnings%20she%20has%20ever%20seen%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaltgrad%20told%20the%20judge%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20negative%20comments%20Lively%20suffered%20in%20early%20August%202024%20coincided%20with%20the%20movie's%20premiere%2C%20another%20Baldoni%20attorney%2C%20Fabien%20Thayamballi%2C%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Lively%20was%20facing%20a%20backlash%20for%20trying%20%26quot%3Bto%20get%20cast%20members%20to%20unfollow%20Baldoni%26quot%3B%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Thayamballi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20faced%20press%20criticism%20for%20cross-promoting%20her%20alcoholic%20beverage%20line%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20premiere%20of%20a%20serious%20movie%20about%20domestic%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20Thayamballi%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaldoni%20is%20also%20fighting%20Lively's%20plan%20to%20call%20an%20expert%20in%20%26quot%3Bbetrayal%20trauma%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Lewis%20J.%20Liman%20said%20he'll%20wait%20to%20decide%20on%20all%20expert%20questions%20until%20the%20sides%20file%20additional%20arguments%20and%20another%20hearing%20is%20held%2C%20set%20for%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjustin-baldoni-blasts-blake-lively-damages-math-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777456801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f111a529fef86fd43d3b6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjustin-baldoni-blasts-blake-lively-damages-math-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Blake%20Lively%20seeks%20more%20than%20%24200M%20from%20Justin%20Baldoni%20at%20next%20month's%20%26quot%3Bretaliation%26quot%3B%20trial.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20his%20side%20challenged%20her%20%26quot%3Bpie%20in%20the%20sky%26quot%3B%20math.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NBA%20set%20for%20major%20rule%20change%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20teams%20losing%20on%20purpose%20for%20better%20draft%20picks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%2