EThis%20quarter's%20busiest%20week%20for%20tech%20earnings%20comes%20at%20a%20precarious%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20AI%20names%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-tech-stocks-selloff-openai-revenue-targets-orcl-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egot%20nailed%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20report%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-missed-targets-what-smart-people-are-saying-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20has%20recently%20missed%20internal%20growth%20targets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Market%20jitters%20over%20that%20news%20will%20collide%20with%20earnings%20today%20from%20Alphabet%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-q1-earnings-preview-aws-amzn-stock-ai-capex-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-q1-earnings-preview-ai-revenue-growth-capex-wall-street-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20the%20already-lofty%20stakes%20around%20the%20reports%20have%20been%20ratcheted%20even%20higher.%20How%20will%20investors%20process%20upcoming%20earnings%20with%20fresh%20doubts%20planted%20in%20their%20minds%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20paints%20a%20bigger%20bullseye%20on%20AI%20capex.%20Magnificent%207%20companies%20have%20pledged%20tens%20of%20billions%20in%20spending%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-microsoft-stock-price-earnings-ai-capex-spending-reaction-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarket%20reactions%20have%20been%20inconsistent%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20traders%20really%20care%20about%20is%20AI%20progress%2C%20and%20they%20favor%20companies%20that%20most%20quickly%20convert%20that%20investment%20into%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ET