will%20also%20be%20watching%20engagement%20trends%2C%20like%20the%20usage%20of%20Gemini%2C%20for%20signs%20of%20how%20AI%20monetization%20is%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENumber%20to%20watch%3A%20Azure%20growth%20rate%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20cloud%20business%20is%20also%20the%20best%20proxy%20for%20its%20AI%20progress.%20Bloomberg%20estimates%20see%2038%25%20sales%20expansion%20for%20Azure%20and%20other%20cloud%20services%2C%20and%2021%25%20Azure%20growth%20attributable%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttention%20will%20also%20be%20paid%20to%20Copilot%20and%20other%20AI%20features.%20Adoption%20is%20rising%2C%20but%20paid%20conversion%20and%20Microsoft's%20ability%20to%20monetize%20are%20still%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapex%20will%20also%20be%20in%20focus%2C%20although%20Microsoft%20has%20largely%20been%20spared%20from%20past%20market%20freak-outs%20because%20of%20its%20comparatively%20strong%20operating%20leverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmazon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENumber%20to%20watch%3A%20AWS%20revenue%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20you%20sensing%20a%20trend%3F%20As%20with%20Alphabet%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20investors%20will%20be%20glued%20to%20the%20cloud%20segment%20for%20signs%20of%20AI%20progress.%20Analysts%20expect%20%2437%20billion%20of%20quarterly%20sales%20from%20the%20business%2C%20a%2025%25%20increase%20from%20the%20year%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEyes%20will%20also%20be%20peeled%20for%20any%20commentary%20or%20tangible%20financial%20impact%20from%20Amazon's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-openai-azure-cloud-computing-backlog-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-profile%20AI-model%20partnerships%3C%2Fa%3E%20(OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20infrastructure%20deals%20(Meta%2C%20Nvidia).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeta%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENumber%20to%20watch%3A%20Ad%20revenue%20growth%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20for%20Meta%20is%20on%20advertising%2C%20rather%20than%20cloud.%20But%20the%20reasoning%20is%20the%20same%20as%20for%20the%20companies%20above%3A%20it's%20the%20business%20that%20should%20see%20the%20most%20immediate%20tangible%20impacts%20of%20AI.%20Meta%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20sales%20of%20%2454%20billion%20for%20the%20segment%2C%20up%2031%25%20from%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20Meta%20is%20the%20least%20diversified%20Magnificent%207%20stock%20%E2%80%94%20driven%20almost%20entirely%20by%20advertising%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-google-meta-microsoft-boost-ai-spending-stocks-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapex-spending%20rebellion%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20investors%20could%20hit%20shares%20to%20a%20disproportionate%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-preview-key-numbers-alphabet-microsoft-amazon-meta-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777456201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f142b83b4f7c3af2b7ae0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-preview-key-numbers-alphabet-microsoft-amazon-meta-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Here's%20what%20to%20watch%20with%20Alphabet%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Meta%20set%20to%20report%20after%20the%20closing%20bell.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jciolli%40businessinsider.com%20(Joe%20Ciolli)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aimee%20Lou%20Wood%20Pokes%20Fun%20at%20%E2%80%98SNL%E2%80%99%20Teeth%20Sketch%20Ahead%20of%20Hosting%20U.K.%20Version%3A%20%E2%80%98This%20Is%20All%20Just%20One%20Big%20Set-Up%20to%20Humiliate%20Me%2C%20Then%3F%E2%80%99%22%2C%22con