finance%2Fbuying-a-pre-owned-rolex-or-omega-the-risk-most-luxury-watch-buyers-ignore-126042900778_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbuying-a-pre-owned-rolex-or-omega-the-risk-most-luxury-watch-buyers-ignore-126042900778_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20agents%20could%20supercharge%20wealth%20advisors%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there's%20still%20a%20memory%20issue%20standing%20in%20the%20way%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22658%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20Dipendra%20Malhotra%2C%20Citi's%20head%20of%20wealth%20technology%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f1359e9244129ecb2f9174%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22494%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDipendra%20Malhotra%2C%20Citi's%20head%20of%20wealth%20technology.%3Cp%3ECiti%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECiti%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-citi-goldman-bofa-wells-how-ai-impact-headcounts-2026%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebetting%20big%20on%20AI%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20its%20wealth%20unit%2C%20including%20unveiling%20a%20new%20AI-powered%20advisor.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bank's%20head%20of%20wealth%20tech%20said%20agents%20across%20the%20industry%20are%20still%20limited%20by%20their%20memory.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20tools%20will%20eventually%2C%20he%20predicts%2C%20help%20sustain%20more%20continuous%20relationships%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECiti%20recently%20added%20a%20high-profile%20new%20wealth%20advisor%20to%20its%20team%20%E2%80%94%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshe's%20AI-generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Citi%20unveiled%20%26quot%3BCiti%20Sky%2C%26quot%3B%20a%2024-hour%20AI-powered%20wealth%20advisor%20that%20will%20start%20getting%20rolled%20out%20this%20summer%20to%20certain%20clients.%20They'll%20be%20able%20to%20ask%20Citi%20Sky%2C%20with%20her%20blue%20blazer%20and%20auburn%20hair%2C%20about%20personalized%20financial%20questions%20and%20market%20insights.%20The%20tool%2C%20which%20Citi's%20Head%20of%20Wealth%20Andy%20Sieg%20predicted%20will%20%26quot%3Bchange%20the%20model%20of%20wealth%20management%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20press%20release%2C%20will%20become%20more%20intuitive%20%26quot%3Bover%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciti-wealth-tech-hire-ai-dipendra-malhotra-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDipendra%20Malhotra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20firm's%20head%20of%20wealth%20technology%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20developing%20the%20tool%2C%20said%20that%20memory%20is%20a%20current%20limitation%20for%20AI%20agents%20in%20wealth%2C%20both%20in%20the%20moment%20and%20in%20the%20long%20term.%20He%20wasn't%20talking%20about%20Citi%20Sky%20specifically%2C%20but%20rather%20the%20broader%20wealth%20management%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20is%20short-term%20memory%3A%20how%20long%20can%20you%20have%20this%20conversation%20before%20you%20start%20hallucinations%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20while%20speaking%20on%20a%20panel%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20New%20York%20Fintech%20Week.%20New%20algorithms%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20likely%20help%20summarize%20conversations%20in%20real%20time%2C%20so%20that%20agents%20can%20talk%20for%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20second%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20have%20long-term%20memory%2C%20and%20that's%20pretty%20much%20all%20conversations%3A%20all%20the%20clicks%2C%20all%20the%20things%20which%20we%20know%20about%20our%20clients%2C%20transactions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20advisors%20keep%20track%20of%20personal%2C%20financial%2C%20and%20political%20events%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgents%20who%20have%20%E2%80%94%20and%20remember%20%E2%80%94%20continuous%20conversations%20with%20clients%20will%20help%20wealth%20advisors%20be%20more%20productive%20and%20sustain%20more%20relationships%2C%20Malhotra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20Nirvana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20memory%20capabilities%20are%20rising.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThat%20kind%20of%20persistent%20awareness%20could%20expand%20the%20number%20of%20clients%20a%20single%20advisor%20can%20effectively%20serve%2C%20he%20adding%20that%20these%20tools%20are%20about%20%26quot%3Bproductivity%20and%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalhotra%20said%20there%20are%20still%20plans%20to%C2%A0hire%20more%20wealth%20advisors%20at%20Citi%2C%20a%20point%20that%20Sieg%20also%20made%20when%20announcing%20Citi%20Sky%2C%20which%20was%20developed%20with%20technology%20from%20Google%20Cloud%20and%20Google%20DeepMind.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAcross%20the%20wealth%20management%20industry%2C%20AI%20is%20being%20deployed%20to%20automate%20grunt%20work%2C%20personalize%20advice%2C%20and%20help%20advisors%20cover%20more%20clients.%20For%20example%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20rolled%20out%20a%20tool%20that%20helps%20its%20advisors%20prepare%20for%2C%20conduct%2C%20and%20follow%20up%20on%20client%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiti%2C%20like%20its%20Wall%20Street%20rivals%2C%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-banks-ai-strategy-jpmorgan-goldman-citi-bofa-2026%23citigroup-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvesting%20in%20generative%20AI%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebeyond%20its%20wealth%20business.%20CEO%20Jane%20Fraser%20said%20on%20an%20earnings%20call%20in%20January%2C%20for%20example%2C%20that%20GenAI%20tools%20had%20saved%20developers%20100%2C000%20hours%20a%20week%20with%20automated%20code%20reviews.%20The%20bank%20spent%20%242.3%20billion%20on%20technology%20and%20communication%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202026%2C%20according%20to%20an%20April%20earnings%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciti-ai-wealth-management-agents-2026-4%5