0and%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%2C%20which%20had%20consumed%20many%20of%20his%20own%20friends.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20small%20effort%20grew%20into%20the%20OSCAR%20(Organization%20for%20Social%20Change%2C%20Awareness%20and%20Responsibility)%20Foundation%20in%202010%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20that%20today%20has%20touched%20thousands%20of%20young%20lives%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20lives%20is%20that%20of%20Yamini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20rainy%20afternoon%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20a%20shy%20Class%209%20student%20walked%20nervously%20into%20a%20ground%20where%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation%20had%20gathered%20children.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496964%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShe%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20sure%20if%20football%20was%20her%20game.%20But%20when%20the%20coach%20handed%20her%20a%20ball%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20kick%20it%20away%20from%20yourself%20and%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20something%20changed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20football%20is%20no%20longer%20just%20a%20sport%20for%20Yamini%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ground%20has%20become%20her%20%E2%80%9Csecond%20home%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20rule%20that%20cha