0very%20well%20through%20this%20humble%20vegetable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20carrots%2C%20he%20also%20cultivates%20rice%20and%20maize%2C%20which%20is%20harvested%20in%20September.%20He%20claims%20to%20earn%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20not%20being%20able%20to%20go%20abroad%20for%20his%20studies%2C%20he%20has%20now%20been%20able%20to%20send%20both%20his%20sons%20abroad%20for%20their%20education%20(one%20of%20whom%20has%20returned%20to%20help%20him)%2C%20bought%20a%20house%2C%20over%2030%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20along%20with%20the%20latest%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20happened%20thanks%20to%20carrot%20farming.%20They%20never%20broke%20my%20heart%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhuman%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20home%20also%20doubles%20up%20as%20a%20carrot%20farming%20school%2C%20where%20he%20helps%20anyone%20interested.%20No%20young%20farmer%20is%20sent%20away%20without%20their%20questions%20being%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20at%20least%20four%20farmers%20who%20come%20home%20daily%20to%20learn.%20I%20explain%20whatever%20I%20know%20in%20detail.%20I%20even%20visit%20their%20farms%20to%20teach%20them%20practically.%20I%E2%80%99m%20always%20available%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20every%20aspiring%20farmer%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20lose%20hope.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20succeed%20is%20determination.%20Nothing%20is%20impossible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EImages%20Courtesy%20Phuman%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757233800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-30-at-11.52.18-1725875918.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20past%2030%20years%2C%20Phuman%20Singh%20Kaurra%20from%20Punjab%20has%20been%20turning%20his%20family's%20fortunes%20around%20through%20carrot%20farming.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20seed%20bank%20that%20can%20cultivate%20up%20to%20650%20acres%20of%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496839%2Fpunjab-farmer-phuman-singh-carrot-farming-earns-crores%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%203%20Million%20Trees%20Brought%20Back%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Forests%2C%20Revived%20Wildlife%20%26amp%3B%20Created%20Jobs%20for%20Thousands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20something%20different%20in%20the%20air%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Inderjit%20Singh%2C%20a%2079-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20cleaner.%20Birds%20sing%20all%20day%2C%20and%20when%20I%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F446298%2Fjunnar-family-revives-forest-digs-70-trenches-plants-450-trees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalk%20through%20the%20trees%20I%20planted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20forest%20that%20belongs%20to%20all%20of%20us.%E2%80%9D%20His%20voice%20carries%20the%20pride%20of%20a%20man%20who%20has%20watched%20life%20return%20to%20land%20once%20left%20barren.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20far%20from%20his%20village%2C%20in%20Lang%2C%2032-year-old%20Romanpreet%20Singh%20shares%20a%20similar%20experience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20imagined%20anything%20could%20grow%20on%20that%20patch%20of%20land%20near%20the%20crematorium.%20It%20was%20dry%20and%20forgotten.%20Now%20it%20is%20buzzing%20with%20butterflies%20and%20birds%2C%20and%20it%20has%20created%20jobs%20for%20women%20and%20youth.%20It%20brought%20our%20village%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20dat