olds%20have%20bright%20yellow%20and%20orange%20petals%20that%20are%20rich%20in%20natural%20pigment%20and%20can%20be%20dried%20and%20ground%20into%20a%20fine%20powder%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fagriplanting.com%2Fhow-to-grow-marigold-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAgri%20Planting%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20their%20vibrant%20colour%2C%20marigolds%20are%20beneficial%20for%20the%20garden%20as%20they%20repel%20pests%20and%20attract%20pollinators.%20The%20flowers%20bloom%20generously%2C%20making%20them%20perfect%20for%20regular%20harvesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Hibiscus%20%E2%80%93%20Red%20and%20pink%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHibiscus%20is%20a%20hardy%2C%20tropical%20shrub%20known%20for%20its%20large%20and%20striking%20blooms%20in%20shades%20of%20red%2C%20pink%2C%20and%20occasionally%20white%20or%20yellow.%20It%20flowers%20throughout%20the%20year%20in%20warmer%20climates%20and%20prefers%20well-watered%20soil%20and%20plenty%20of%20sunlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20rangoli%20powder%2C%20the%20petals%20should%20be%20dried%20in%20the%20shade%20to%20preserve%20their%20colour%20before%20being%20ground%20to%20a%20fine%20consistency.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F473545%2Fgrow-hibiscus-in-balcony-guide-benefits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHibiscus%20flowers%20also%20attract%20butterflies%20and%20bees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20the%20garden%20into%20a%20lively%20and%20colourful%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Turmeric%20%E2%80%93%20Bright%20yellow%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurmeric%20is%20a%20traditional%20root%20crop%20that%20grows%20from%20rhizomes%20and%20thrives%20in%20warm%2C%20humid%20weather%20with%20partial%20shade.%20It%20takes%20around%20seven%20to%20nine%20months%20to%20mature%2C%20but%20the%20wait%20is%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20harvested%2C%20the%20roots%20can%20be%20sliced%2C%20sun-dried%2C%20and%20ground%20into%20a%20rich%20yellow%20powder%20with%20a%20warm%2C%20earthy%20tone.%20Turmeric%20is%20also%20widely%20used%20in%20cooking%20and%20medicine%2C%20making%20it%20a%20practical%20and%20rewarding%20addition%20to%20any%20rangoli%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Beetroot%20%E2%80%93%20Purple%20and%20deep%20pink%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeetroot%20is%20a%20cool-season%20vegetable%20that%20grows%20well%20in%20soft%2C%20well-aerated%20soil.%20It%20can%20be%20easily%20grown%20from%20seed%20and%20reaches%20maturity%20in%20just%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-26T191841.367_11zon-1756216134.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Even%20the%20peel%20and%20leafy%20tops%20of%20the%20beetroot%20plant%20contain%20colour%2C%20so%20you%20can%20use%20them%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20myBageecha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-26T191841.367_11zon-1756216134.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-26T191841.367_11zon-1756216134-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-26T191841.367_11zon-1756216134-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-0